data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Markland neighborhood of St. Johns County, FL! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence, built by Dream Finders, offers a wealth of luxury features.  Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly blends elegance and functionality. The main level boasts a spacious living area, a gourmet kitchen, dining room, eat in kitchen, butler's pantry, and an office. The primary suite is on the main level and is a true retreat with spa-like bathroom.  Upstairs, you'll find a cozy loft area that can be used as a playroom, media room, or additional living space. All 3 remaining bedrooms are upstairs along with two more full bathrooms.  Outside, the enclosed lanai provides a perfect spot for outdoor entertaining or relaxation, while the detached garage offers parking convenience and extra storage space.
Don't miss this opportunity to own a premium home in a gated community known for its amenities and prime location.
